<Base title="Interface Programming" description="Interface programming – simply integrate existing system landscapes with Shopware 6 by Hob by Horse.">
<div class="lp"><section class="hero"><div class="hi">
<p class="kicker">E-Commerce</p>
<h1>Interface Programming – Simply Integrate Existing System Landscapes</h1>
<p>With interface programming, you don't have to overhaul the system landscape of your online shop. Instead, you can simply integrate accounting software, merchandise management systems or marketplaces with Shopware 6. Extensions are individually possible at any time.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>Features of Interface Programming by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>Interfaces are tools in the online shop for all goods processes and customer communications. These include payment, ERP and CRM, shipping and fulfilment, legal, search and recommendations, as well as email marketing and much more. In an existing online shop, such a comprehensive shop system would have to be completely rebuilt. With the technologies of Shopware 6, you can restructure existing processes and benefit from the extensions in the future.</p>

<h2>Integrations in the Shopware Shop with Interface Programming</h2>
<p>These programming details are implemented by Hob by Horse with interface programming for your online shop:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Payment, Shipping and Fulfilment:</strong> Modern payment methods for various target group habits improve the acceptance of your online shop. Shipping processes also run quickly and smoothly.</li>
<li><strong>Multichannel and PIM:</strong> Information from your online shop reaches the target group with better communication and sales strategies. Product information of even complex scope is efficiently processed and published on your channels.</li>
<li><strong>ERP and CRM:</strong> Through software-based resource planning, you can calculate more precisely via central databases. Customer data is stored, their interactions tracked and saved for analysis purposes.</li>
<li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Via a tracking code in the page code of your online shop, a statistical overview of all traffic processes is possible.</li>
<li><strong>Marketing Automation and Email Marketing:</strong> Both programming details establish customer contact from the first point of contact and automate customer support beyond the purchase process.</li>
<li><strong>Loyalty and Rewards:</strong> With this you organise your discount campaigns as a programmed reward system based on purchase value or customer loyalty, as well as access to preferred products or services.</li>
<li><strong>Legal, Search and Reco:</strong> Legally relevant content of your online shop is kept up to date, as is the visibility of your e-commerce based on certified ratings on corresponding rating platforms such as Trustpilot.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Relevant Industries for Interface Programming with Shopware 6</h2>
<p>Retail benefits from this programming just as much as every online shop in the trade areas of crafts, lifestyle, beauty, hospitality and gastronomy, or automotive, machinery and tools. For every online shop, fast processes mean more focus on the needs of the target group and less effort in personnel and processing time.</p>

<h2>Benefits of Interface Programming by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>Your B2B target groups benefit from our interface programming through fast access and fast process flows, enabling seamless project planning. In B2C, consumers rely on the various integrated tools that make selection, shopping and ordering processes easier at internet speed. Online shop operators can concentrate on their core business, which can grow faster and more efficiently thanks to freed-up resources.</p>
<p>Would you like to modernise your online shop with interface programming or start completely new with Shopware 6? Call Hob by Horse or arrange an appointment by email!</p>
</div></div>
